SymptomCounter - Class in com.hemebiotech.analytics
Implements ISymptomAnalyzer to count symptoms and return a list of strings with symptoms and their number of occurrences, sorted alphabetically by default or with a custom comparator
SymptomCounter() - Constructor for class com.hemebiotech.analytics.SymptomCounter
Default constructor: Set comparator to sort symptoms alphabetically
SymptomCounter(Comparator<String>) - Constructor for class com.hemebiotech.analytics.SymptomCounter
Parametric constructor: Set a custom comparator to sort symptoms
Symptoms - Class in com.hemebiotech.analytics
This class encapsulate all the logic to read raw symptom data from a source, analyze it, and write the result into a target
Symptoms(ISymptomReader, ISymptomAnalyzer, ISymptomWriter) - Constructor for class com.hemebiotech.analytics.Symptoms
This constructor set the implementation of the read, analyze and write logic that will be used by this class
